 |-Module/

 follows terraform module dir method to create aws cluod infrastrcuture with Root module and Child Module
 for reuseable code ready to use.

 the child module has resources defined with 
 > aws instance ami, region, key-apir, type, creats a security group for ingress and egress of ssh and http kind
 > creates an ebs vol and configures volume and attaches to the instance in same region